00:13:25.570 --> 00:13:30.760
At some point it ruins
the game to do that.

00:13:30.760 --> 00:13:32.300
If your going to have people
cheating, they're going to

00:13:32.300 --> 00:13:34.350
find a way to cheat, anyways.

00:13:34.350 --> 00:13:38.320
