down as much as you can to

00:14:00.010 --> 00:14:03.220
ensure that what somebody does
is what everybody sees.

00:14:03.220 --> 00:14:05.950
But then beyond that to leave
it as loose as possible, to

00:14:05.950 --> 00:14:09.155
that works for everyone.

00:14:09.155 --> 00:14:10.770
