Bruce Cordell is the
blue person, I'm in

00:15:33.090 --> 00:15:35.270
there over to the right.

00:15:35.270 --> 00:15:36.950
And this is what we've
all discovered.

00:15:36.950 --> 00:15:37.430
And this is what we've
all discovered.

00:15:37.430 --> 00:15:41.220
